title: The Yellow Deli
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Locations in several states and one in Canada. Offers a vegan burger in a make-your-own sandwich option with several vegan breads and spreads available, salads with vegan house dressing, fruit bowls, iced tea with organic sugar, juice bar, and coffee.
